Trade/Device Name(s): Quest Diagnostics Urine Cocaine Metabolite EIA
Regulation Name(s): Cocaine and cocaine metabolite test system
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Quest Diagnostics Urine Cocaine Metabolite EIA, a competitive enzyme immunoassay for qualitative screening of benzoylecgonine in urine.
Indications for Use Summary: Qualitative detection of benzoylecgonine, the primary metabolite of cocaine, in human urine on automated clinical chemistry analyzers for laboratory in vitro diagnostic use.
